<html>
  <head>
    <title>Hensgen Holiday Wishes 2011</title>
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Bilbo+Swash+Caps' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <style>
      body {
        color: #740000;
        font-family: 'Bilbo Swash Caps', cursive;
        font-size: 2em;
        background-color: #ebc5c5;
        text-align: center;
        width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        margin: 20px 0 0 0;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 42px;
        margin: 0px;
      }
      img {
        -webkit-border-radius: 3px;
        -moz-border-radius: 3px;
        border-radius: 3px;
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
      #left {
        width: 250px;
        padding: 0 10px;
        float: left;
        text-align: right;
      }
      #center {
        float: left;
        width: 400px;
        padding: 0 10px;
        background-color: #fff;
      }
      #right {
        width: 250px;
        padding: 0 10px;
        float: left;
        text-align: left;
      }
      p {
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-top: 500px;
      }
      p.first {
        margin-top: 250px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id='left'>
      <p class='first'>
        We'd like to say we took our Christmas card online this year to save a tree, but we really just procrastinated too long.
      </p>
      <p>We got a new job.</p>
      <p>We learned to swim.</p>
      <p>We went on vacation</p>
    </div>
    <div id='center'>
      <h1>Hensgen Holiday Wishes</h1>
      <h2>2011</h2>
      <% Dir.glob('public/images/*.jpg').each do |path| %>
        <img border="0" alt="" src="images/<%= File.basename(path) %>"/><br>
      <% end %>
      <h2>Happy New Year!</h2>
      <h1>Love,</h1>
      <img src='signature_nick.png' style='width:100px'/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='signature_mia.png' style='width:100px'/><br/>
      <img src='signature_jenni.png' style='width:100px'/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='signature_dan.png' style='width:100px'/>
    </div>
    <div id='right'>
      <p>We learned to ride bikes.</p>
      <p>We got a new job.</p>
      <p>We learned to swim.</p>
      <p>We went on vacation</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
